We may process your personal data for the following purposes: 
• To provide our services in accordance with the applicable terms;
• To manage the business relationship with you and the client of RG Relocation Genevoise SA that you represent;
• To develop and improve our services;
 and to provide information and offers to current or potential clients of RG Relocation Genevoise SA through selected third parties. Any marketing materials distributed using your personal data are sent to you as a representative of a current or potential corporate client of RG Relocation Genevoise SA and not as a private individual.
